casebody.data:
Nancy White VENCIL, petitioner,
v.
PENNSYLVANIA STATE POLICE, et al. No. 16-1253. Supreme Court of the United States June 26, 2017.

Motion of Autistic Self Advocacy Network, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Pennsylvania, Middle District denied.
